column4: question about the mplayer=skins package, how come it doesnt add any extra skins to mplayer?, also when i do a search for it in my system via aptitude search mplayer-skins i get this - > i A mplayer-skins- Skins for the Ubuntu mplayer Package, i kno the i stands for installed, what does the A stand for?
